<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: black;
            color: tan;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #D2B48C;
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        main section {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to CU Boulder Class Finder</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <p>CU Boulder Class Finder is your one-stop destination for discovering and enrolling in the perfect classes for your academic needs at the University of Colorado Boulder. Whether you're a new student or an existing one, we help you explore the course offerings across various disciplines and find the right courses to fulfill your academic goals.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h2>How to Use</h2>
            <p>Start your search for classes using the navigation bar above, or explore the latest offerings in the <a href="/classes" style="color: tan;">Classes</a> section.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Add Trending section here -->
        <header>
            <h1>Trending Classes</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="container text-center">
            {{#each trendingClasses}}
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    {{name}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
